What you need to know:  The Italian was to face the Kenyan for the first time over the distance at the Kip Keino Classic at the Moi International Sports Centre Kasarani on May 7, but was hospitalized for gastrointestinal problems.His coach Paolo Camossi noted that Jacobs would not be able to show up at the starting blocks because he was still under observation in the emergency room of the Ruaraka Uhai Neema Hospital, managed by the Italian NGO World Friends.